Package: hellmer
Title: Batch Processing for 'ellmer' Chat Models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Dylan", "Pieper", , "dylanpieper@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides batch processing capabilities for chat models from the 'ellmer' 
    package. Implements safe state handling and efficient batch operations using 'S7' 
    for object-oriented programming. Includes progress tracking, structured data 
    extraction, and flexible output control.
